{"tid":595802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工資中位數升至1.68萬　男多女三成","createTime":"2018-03-17T04:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T07:39:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"81cd1b16774c9aa691caa8e819288ed94229c607","tid":595802,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T04:39:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180317/20334634\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180317%2F20334634&d=fZM7N6QrlwatQABWD2VYM0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=a9f7fdc4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180317%2F20334634&h=fecf7280\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180317/20334634</a><br />\n<br />\n工資中位數升至1.68萬　男多女三成<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180317/large/16735804.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180317%2Flarge%2F16735804.jpg&h=f38c36a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n調查顯示，35至44歲僱員的每月工資中位數最高，達19,700元。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】受惠於最低工資去年上調，本港僱員的工資中位數相應提高。統計處昨發表「2017年收入及工時按年調查」，數據顯示，去年5至6月本港僱員每月工資中位數為16,800元，較前年同期上升4.1%。<br />\n<br />\n男僱員月薪中位數達19,100元，較去女僱員的14,700元多出近三成。各行業中，以飲食業加薪幅度最高，去年5至6月的每月工資中位數為12,400元，較前年同期高出5.7%；其次為零售業，去年每月工資中位數為13,000元，升幅4.8%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平均時薪68元<br />\n<br />\n調查顯示，介乎35歲至44歲的僱員的每月工資中位數最高，達19,700元，其次是介乎25歲至34歲的僱員，有17,600元，人工最低則是15至24歲僱員，每月工資中位數12,400元。學歷越高，搵錢能力越強，專上程度學歷僱員每月工資中位數26,400元，小學及以下程度則只有11,500元。<br />\n<br />\n若以時薪計算，去年5至6月本港僱員的每小時工資中位數為68元，較前年同期高4%。政府去年5月將最低工資由32.5元提高至34.5元，報告顯示有26,700名僱員正賺取最低工資，即時薪34.5元。<br />\n<br />\n■記者盧文烈"},{"pid":"e6f7c91d8b1c469001beb12d1995d53910670bf0","tid":595802,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T04:43:50.000Z","msg":"低於標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a584efab1bd38069f4c89913169e4c832c93ad0c","tid":595802,"uid":609,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T04:54:39.000Z","msg":"專上程度學歷僱員每月工資中位數26,400元<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e1a49df4ce4a7e23d5054efe6c984d26e0742a","tid":595802,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T04:56:06.000Z","msg":"婦權份子又可以大叫唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f634d31205240e12d14de9dc62030f61258d8d03","tid":595802,"uid":153811,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a584efab1bd38069f4c89913169e4c832c93ad0c","tid":595802,"uid":609,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T04:54:39.000Z","msg":"專上程度學歷僱員每月工資中位數26,400元<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T04:56:33.000Z","msg":"用左2年半先過到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6276483da9d968edde5bdfa2f6eaf48c6f03422","tid":595802,"uid":108236,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a584efab1bd38069f4c89913169e4c832c93ad0c","tid":595802,"uid":609,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T04:54:39.000Z","msg":"專上程度學歷僱員每月工資中位數26,400元<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T04:59:06.000Z","ms